<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR1h0004-en-d69cdc0a" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>論語新解</title><editor role="translator">Qian Mu 錢穆</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>論語新解</title>九州出版社，2001</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR1h0004"><title xml:lang="och">論語</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2023-10-31T18:37:25.752+09:00</date> by CH</creation><creation resp="#CH">Header modified: <date>2023-10-31T19:24:37.425+09:00</date> by CH</creation><creation resp="#CH">Header modified: <date>2024-01-25T07:32:13.233+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR1h0004-start"><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T18:47:02.373+09:00">Recognising the presence here of two different types of quotation marks is crucial for an understanding of this passage.  The crucial question is whether this is just an autobiographic description or in fact an abstract reference to an ethical generalisation. "Was Du nicht magst dass man Dir tu, das fueg auch keinem andern zu!" Zong Fubang sub verbo 加：(3)　譄、誣、〜三字同義。《論語．公冶⻑》「我不欲⼈之～諸我也」劉寶楠正義引段⽟裁云｜《說⽂．⼒部》段⽟裁注：「說⽂：～，語相譄〜也。譄下⽈〜也，誣下⽈〜也。此云語相譄〜也。知譄、誣、〜三字同義矣。誣⼈⽈譄，亦⽈～。」　(27)毁譽不以實皆⽈〜也。《說⽂．⾔部》「誣，〜也」段⽟裁注。　(75)～諸，盖飾辭，毁⼈之謂。《論語．公冶長》「我不欲⼈之～諸我也」劉寶楠正義引沈⽒濤《論語注辨偽》⽈。　　NB：The parallel use of 加 ACT in LY 4.6 seems to makes all this unnecessary.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:29:06.445+09:00">吾亦不要把这些来加在别人身上。”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:29:12.057+09:00">先生说：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:29:20.277+09:00">“赐呀！</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:29:29.109+09:00">这非你能力所及呀！”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:51:18.708+09:00">先生说：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:51:27.919+09:00">“我没有见到喜好于仁</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:51:37.754+09:00">和僧恶于不仁的人。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:51:43.603+09:00">若果喜好于仁了，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:51:56.164+09:00">他自会觉得世上更没有事物能胜过于仁的了。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:52:02.593+09:00">若能憎恶于不仁，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:52:09.99+09:00">那人也就是仁人了，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:52:21.557+09:00">因他将不让那些不仁的事物加在他身上。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:52:29.845+09:00">真有人肯化一天之力来用在仁上吗？</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:52:35.998+09:00">我没见过力有不足的。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_004-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T17:52:46.463+09:00">或许世上真有苦力不足的人，但我终是未见啊。”</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:12:34.849+09:00">先生说：</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:12:41.68+09:00">“由呀！</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:12:45.337+09:00">我教你怎么算知道吧！</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:12:51.275+09:00">你知道你所知，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:13:01.047+09:00">又能同时知道你所不知，</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-19a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:13:01.337+09:00">才算是知。”</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>